      "id": "PopularPost37936",
      "post_content": "Actually, shady, you always had to tap it to use it. If you look at the artifact cards in Alpha and Beta, you'll see that some are called Mono Artifacts (which the IM is) and some are called Poly Artifacts.\n  \n   \nPoly Artifacts do not tap when you use them.\n  \n   \nMono Artifacts DO tap when you use them.",
      "posted_by": "DarthMeatloaf",
